@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
actor "LP / Trader" as User
rectangle "config\n(pool PDA)" as Config
rectangle "vault_x" as Vx
rectangle "vault_y" as Vy
rectangle "mint_lp" as LP
Config --> Vx : reserve X
Config --> Vy : reserve Y
Config --> LP : LP supply
User ..> Vx : adds / swaps X
User ..> Vy : adds / swaps Y
User ..> LP : holds LP shares
@enduml
